bc236-4 gKlMxC">Save</span></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-3 iOJnhy eIqCxs">essay</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-2 iOJnhy llXHdp">Nations and empires</p></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-10 tdBWn">A United States of Europe</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-11 hYbLtW">A free and unified Europe was first imagined by Italian radicals in the 19th century. Could we yet see their dream made real?</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-12 iOJnhy dFhhBp">Fernanda Gallo</p></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-6 kQroYe"></div></div></a><a href="/essays/what-role-for-revenge-in-jewish-life-literature-and-culture"><div class="sc-d56bc236-9 iGZwDd"><div type="essay" class="sc-82db9615-2 jowSfL"><img alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/004a5cb4-3895-4343-a58c-a9a949542994/essay-jewish-resistance-national-library-of-israel.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/004a5cb4-3895-4343-a58c-a9a949542994/essay-jewish-resistance-national-library-of-israel.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/004a5cb4-3895-4343-a58c-a9a949542994/essay-jewish-resistance-national-library-of-israel.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/004a5cb4-3895-4343-a58c-a9a949542994/essay-jewish-resistance-national-library-of-israel.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/004a5cb4-3895-4343-a58c-a9a949542994/essay-jewish-resistance-national-library-of-israel.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/004a5cb4-3895-4343-a58c-a9a949542994/essay-jewish-resistance-national-library-of-israel.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://im